column14: Ice MMT (0.5) approx 30m U/S of GH.  Upon arrival - HG bouncing quite a bit.  Initial DWL to determine SRC.  Following initial DWL, ice was removed to evaluate the status of the orifice tip.  As ice was removed the HG scroll was stsbilizing.   2nd DWL, cut from MP CLAMP, HG had stabilized by then.  Purged, no change.  Following 3rd DWL and no stability with logger HG, decided to replace the FTS bubbler (@1146). Logger reset (new bubbbler @ 0953). Following install of new bubbler the logger HG was holding steady, no bounce at all.  Mid-section
